Tonight, it's all on me.

00:15:36.033 --> 00:15:38.402
As a way of asking you
to be nice to Il Ri.

00:15:38.802 --> 00:15:40.904
Excuse me, could we get the menu here?

00:15:42.239 --> 00:15:44.808
Your new boyfriend is so cool,
Deputy Editor.

00:15:44.808 --> 00:15:45.609
The best.

00:15:45.843 --> 00:15:47.878
Then we can order
something expensive, right?

00:15:47.878 --> 00:15:49.113
Of course.

00:15:49.113 --> 00:15:50.848
Just order whatever you want.

00:15:52.016 --> 00:15:52.983
Okay.

00:15:56.587 --> 00:15:57.554
Wait, Il Ri.

00:15:58.222 --> 00:15:59.056
Come here a sec.

00:16:00.224 --> 00:16:03.460
Why is your face so red?
Are you not feeling well?

00:16:03.460 --> 00:16:05.296
- No...
- Hold still.

00:16:08.632 --> 00:16:10.801
You're burning up.

00:16:10.801 --> 00:16:11.669
No, I'm...

00:16:11.669 --> 00:16:13.604
Are you okay, baby?

00:16:14.905 --> 00:16:16.407
I don't want you to get sick.

00:16:34.024 --> 00:16:35.025
This is embarrassing.

00:16:35.359 --> 00:16:37.494
I was blushing like crazy.

00:16:38.262 --> 00:16:40.130
What is Sang Gyu thinking?

00:16:41.031 --> 00:16:43.233
Whatever. I'll just play along for now.

00:16:44.001 --> 00:16:45.903
It'd be weird to suddenly say
it was a lie.

00:16:51.942 --> 00:16:52.943
Be honest.

00:16:53.877 --> 00:16:55.079
He's not really your boyfriend, is he?

00:16:55.779 --> 00:16:56.647
Why do you care?

00:16:57.681 --> 00:16:59.717
People say tastes change with age.

00:16:59.717 --> 00:17:02.086
So do you like someone local
and old-fashioned now?

00:17:02.086 --> 00:17:04.054
My taste used to be pretty terrible.

00:17:04.555 --> 00:17:06.190
I'm just trying to upgrade.

00:17:08.192 --> 00:17:09.426
We need to talk.

00:17:09.727 --> 00:17:11.095
I have nothing to say, so get lost.

00:17:12.129 --> 00:17:13.731
I said let's talk.

00:17:13.731 --> 00:17:15.332
- Let go!
- Il Ri.

00:17:16.767 --> 00:17:18.869
What do you think you're doing
to my girlfriend?

00:17:21.305 --> 00:17:22.206
Let go of me.

00:17:24.141 --> 00:17:25.309
I said let go.

00:17:31.382 --> 00:17:32.216
Hey.

00:17:33.851 --> 00:17:35.185
The past is the past.

00:17:36.553 --> 00:17:38.355
It's already over between you two,
isn't it?

00:17:39.690 --> 00:17:41.525
Aren't you ashamed
in front of your current girlfriend?

00:17:47.431 --> 00:17:48.265
Damn it.

00:17:57.274 --> 00:17:58.142
Let's go.

00:17:58.642 --> 00:17:59.710
Honey, where are you going?

00:17:59.710 --> 00:18:01.612
- Come.
- Honey.

00:18:01.946 --> 00:18:02.846
Eom Jong Do.

00:18:03.981 --> 00:18:05.916
He's so annoying.

00:18:08.118 --> 00:18:09.987
Those guys.

00:18:10.287 --> 00:18:12.790
Look at all this food they ordered
that they're not even going to eat.

00:18:34.678 --> 00:18:35.946
Right.

00:18:35.946 --> 00:18:37.982
I need to make a quick call.

00:18:37.982 --> 00:18:39.550
Do you guys want to go first?

00:18:39.550 --> 00:18:41.085
Go on, I'll be right behind you.

00:18:41.085 --> 00:18:41.986
Hey!

00:18:42.519 --> 00:18:44.321
We'll wait for you.
Come when you're done.

00:18:50.728 --> 00:18:52.830
Do you want to sit on that bench
for a bit while we wait?

00:18:53.430 --> 00:18:54.531
Yes.

00:18:54.531 --> 00:18:55.366
Over there.

00:19:15.152 --> 00:19:16.587
Thanks for today, dude.

00:19:18.088 --> 00:19:19.690
I didn't do anything.

00:19:20.424 --> 00:19:21.492
He seemed strange.

00:19:23.127 --> 00:19:25.629
But still,
you pretended to be my boyfriend...

00:19:25.629 --> 00:19:27.064
when you like someone else.

00:19:28.999 --> 00:19:29.767
Pretended?

00:19:31.969 --> 00:19:35.239
That sounds kind of sad.

00:19:36.006 --> 00:19:37.975
Why? It's true.

00:19:38.742 --> 00:19:40.978
I feel sorry for whoever it is.

00:19:42.179 --> 00:19:43.314
Did you tell her how you feel?

00:19:44.548 --> 00:19:45.349
No.

00:19:46.483 --> 00:19:47.318
Why not?

00:19:48.352 --> 00:19:52.289
I just feel like I need some time.

00:19:53.090 --> 00:19:54.024
For what?

00:19:56.126 --> 00:19:58.595
I need time to think...

00:19:59.530 --> 00:20:02.533
about what I should say
to best express my feelings.

00:20:04.902 --> 00:20:05.936
Lucky her.

00:20:06.270 --> 00:20:07.805
You're so serious.

00:20:08.405 --> 00:20:09.940
Who is it? Someone I know?

00:20:16.347 --> 00:20:17.181
Hey.

00:20:18.415 --> 00:20:20.851
Do you really not know,
or are you pretending not to know?

00:20:24.254 --> 00:20:25.389
You knew...

00:20:26.490 --> 00:20:27.925
I liked you.

00:20:28.926 --> 00:20:30.027
And you know...

00:20:31.128 --> 00:20:33.797
I still like you.

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:39.370
It's been 20 years
since we met again like this, right?

00:20:41.772 --> 00:20:42.973
It's crazy.

00:20:45.042 --> 00:20:45.943
Are you...

00:20:47.678 --> 00:20:48.712
Lee Il Ri?

00:20:52.816 --> 00:20:53.550
Hey.

00:20:55.986 --> 00:20:58.155
Hey, are you okay?

00:20:58.789 --> 00:21:00.491
The moment I saw you that day,

00:21:01.025 --> 00:21:03.594
it felt like I'd gotten in a time machine.

00:21:04.295 --> 00:21:05.729
I knew right away.

00:21:08.232 --> 00:21:09.300
In my whole life,

00:21:10.301 --> 00:21:12.503
I'd never liked anyone
as much as I liked you.

00:21:16.206 --> 00:21:17.541
Unbelievable.

00:21:20.644 --> 00:21:24.014
I wanted to confess to you
in a really cool way,

00:21:25.249 --> 00:21:26.150
but I failed.

00:21:29.186 --> 00:21:31.055
Since it's already come to this,
I guess there's nothing we can do.

00:21:36.226 --> 00:21:37.061
Il Ri.

00:21:39.663 --> 00:21:40.564
How about you?

00:21:41.799 --> 00:21:42.733
What do you think of me?

00:21:45.603 --> 00:21:48.639
How about dating me?

00:21:53.177 --> 00:21:54.578
You don't want to?

00:22:00.117 --> 00:22:01.485
It's not exactly that.

00:22:01.485 --> 00:22:03.687
Then what's making you hesitate?

00:22:08.759 --> 00:22:09.693
It's just...

00:22:12.930 --> 00:22:13.764
No.

00:22:14.832 --> 00:22:16.433
You don't have to answer right now.

00:22:17.301 --> 00:22:19.403
Take your time and think it over,

00:22:22.473 --> 00:22:23.807
and maybe feel a little pressure too.

00:22:36.220 --> 00:22:37.054
What's that?

00:22:44.128 --> 00:22:45.796
Should we ride this back home?

00:22:52.770 --> 00:22:55.739
I can't believe it.
Sang Gyu is such a macho man.

00:22:56.206 --> 00:22:58.609
Hey, come to think of it,

00:22:58.609 --> 00:23:01.045
I remembered how Sang Gyu was
always looking out just for you...

00:23:01.045 --> 00:23:02.680
back in college.

00:23:03.547 --> 00:23:04.615
What's with that face?

00:23:04.949 --> 00:23:05.950
Is something wrong?

00:23:07.084 --> 00:23:08.218
I don't know.

00:23:08.719 --> 00:23:10.387
What do you mean, you don't know?

00:23:10.654 --> 00:23:12.122
Don't tell me you don't like Sang Gyu.

00:23:14.291 --> 00:23:15.693
It's not like that.

00:23:19.163 --> 00:23:20.197
(Eom Jong Do)

00:23:20.197 --> 00:23:22.700
Why is this punk calling
in the middle of the night?

00:23:22.900 --> 00:23:23.901
Pick up.

00:23:25.636 --> 00:23:26.470
What?

00:23:27.104 --> 00:23:28.839
Put it on speaker.

00:23:31.342 --> 00:23:32.276
Il Ri.

00:23:32.643 --> 00:23:34.278
How could you change like that so fast?

00:23:35.079 --> 00:23:36.513
Was that really all
our relationship meant to you?

00:23:37.548 --> 00:23:38.849
What are you even talking about right now?

00:23:39.283 --> 00:23:41.051
I still like you, Il Ri.

00:23:42.686 --> 00:23:44.922
I felt like crap
the whole way over to my place.

00:23:44.922 --> 00:23:47.191
After I saw that guy last time,
I couldn't even sleep.

00:23:47.191 --> 00:23:48.292
I kept wondering why I was like that,

00:23:49.827 --> 00:23:52.096
and then I realized.

00:23:52.630 --> 00:23:53.764
I'm really sorry,

00:23:55.332 --> 00:23:56.734
but I still love you, Il Ri.

00:24:00.070 --> 00:24:02.139
I know I've messed up.

00:24:02.873 --> 00:24:05.342
But it wasn't that I didn't like you.

00:24:05.342 --> 00:24:06.977
I was scared of getting married.

00:24:07.645 --> 00:24:10.214
I was crushed by the weight of having
to take responsibility for someone,

00:24:10.214 --> 00:24:12.850
so I ran away like a coward.

00:24:14.118 --> 00:24:16.020
But that happens, right?

00:24:16.020 --> 00:24:17.755
People do that sometimes,

00:24:17.755 --> 00:24:18.622
right?

00:24:18.622 --> 00:24:19.857
Sure, it happens.

00:24:20.591 --> 00:24:22.993
But a guy who actually does that...

00:24:22.993 --> 00:24:24.795
really is a total bastard.

00:24:25.763 --> 00:24:26.664
I know.

00:24:28.098 --> 00:24:29.166
So I'm sorry.

00:24:30.000 --> 00:24:30.968
I'm really sorry.

00:24:31.835 --> 00:24:33.470
I must've lost my mind for a while.

00:24:34.505 --> 00:24:35.739
What are you trying to say?

00:24:37.074 --> 00:24:40.144
I'll break up with So Young.
So you break up with that jerk too,

00:24:41.912 --> 00:24:43.113
and marry me.

00:24:46.917 --> 00:24:50.087
Are you apologizing right now,
or proposing?

00:24:50.087 --> 00:24:51.855
Does it bother you that much
that I'm seeing someone?

00:24:52.189 --> 00:24:54.091
Enough that you want to stop it
with marriage?

00:24:54.091 --> 00:24:55.259
It's because I like you that much.

00:24:55.259 --> 00:24:57.194
I'm saying I'll even marry you.

00:24:57.194 --> 00:24:58.062
Don't you get it?

00:24:58.629 --> 00:24:59.630
So,

00:25:00.965 --> 00:25:02.166
let's start over.

00:25:03.167 --> 00:25:04.935
I'll really treat you right
this time, okay?

00:25:08.505 --> 00:25:09.907
Hey, why'd you hang up?

00:25:10.574 --> 00:25:13.444
Hearing that bastard beg like that
is so satisfying.

00:25:13.811 --> 00:25:15.679
I don't even need to hear it.

00:25:18.882 --> 00:25:21.185
No matter how hard I try to hide my charm,

00:25:21.185 --> 00:25:22.853
it just won't stay hidden.

00:25:22.853 --> 00:25:26.090
Why can't anyone get over me,
and they keep clinging like this?

00:25:26.090 --> 00:25:27.958
Are you bragging right now?

00:25:31.462 --> 00:25:32.630
I'm jealous.

00:25:33.197 --> 00:25:34.798
Back when I was single,

00:25:34.798 --> 00:25:37.101
I had guys flocking to me left and right.

00:25:38.435 --> 00:25:39.270
Hey.

00:25:39.803 --> 00:25:42.539
Don't you think
I've been looking younger lately?

00:25:43.707 --> 00:25:44.742
Is it because of this?

00:25:44.742 --> 00:25:47.278
Hey! Go easy on that!

00:25:47.711 --> 00:25:48.979
You're so stingy.

00:25:58.789 --> 00:26:00.457
(Sweet Home Shopping)

00:26:05.496 --> 00:26:07.531
Did you hear about Seon Min?

00:26:08.265 --> 00:26:09.066
Ye Na.

00:26:10.100 --> 00:26:11.769
Do you really think it's right
to just stay quiet like this?

00:26:13.070 --> 00:26:14.505
Keeping the truth buried any longer.

00:26:14.505 --> 00:26:16.607
Don't you think that's way too unfair
to Seon Min?

00:26:18.475 --> 00:26:20.444
But I only heard it secondhand,

00:26:20.444 --> 00:26:22.179
so it doesn't carry any weight
when I say it.

00:26:22.179 --> 00:26:23.047
That's why I really hope you...

00:26:23.047 --> 00:26:24.248
I told you before.

00:26:25.516 --> 00:26:26.517
I...

00:26:26.817 --> 00:26:28.686
never had anything like that happen to me.

00:26:29.520 --> 00:26:32.022
Why do you keep trying to drag me
into something so filthy?

00:26:32.022 --> 00:26:34.124
What on earth did you hear from her?

00:26:34.124 --> 00:26:36.126
I get that this puts you
in a tough spot, but...

00:26:36.126 --> 00:26:37.261
Who do you think you are, Producer?

00:26:38.395 --> 00:26:41.065
Were you seriously dating
Seon Min or something?

00:26:41.065 --> 00:26:44.101
Or do you just enjoy playing the hero?

00:26:44.935 --> 00:26:46.870
Why are you trying to meddle
in someone else's life?

00:26:46.870 --> 00:26:47.871
Song Ye Na.

00:26:50.774 --> 00:26:53.911
Why do you think
Seon Min tried to kill herself?

00:26:56.347 --> 00:26:57.414
Maybe Seon Min...

00:26:58.115 --> 00:26:59.984
actually wanted to bury all of that...

00:27:00.884 --> 00:27:02.820
and go back to living like before.

00:27:03.354 --> 00:27:04.488
But then,

00:27:04.488 --> 00:27:06.056
you stuck your nose in for no reason,

00:27:06.590 --> 00:27:09.159
and things blew up beyond repair.

00:27:09.526 --> 00:27:11.762
And when you couldn't take responsibility,
you backed out!

00:27:12.463 --> 00:27:14.298
How do you think
Seon Min felt at that moment?

00:27:16.166 --> 00:27:17.735
In the end, what pushed her that far...

00:27:18.235 --> 00:27:19.970
wasn't Kim Jeong Sik, but you.

00:27:20.404 --> 00:27:21.505
So...

00:27:22.373 --> 00:27:23.440
please,

00:27:24.742 --> 00:27:26.944
stop pretending to be some good guy
and just stay out of it.

00:27:40.724 --> 00:27:41.792
What happened to Seon Min?

00:27:41.792 --> 00:27:42.760
How is she?

00:27:44.128 --> 00:27:46.764
Her vital signs are back to normal,

00:27:47.498 --> 00:27:49.199
but she still won't wake up.

00:27:49.199 --> 00:27:50.601
The doctor says it's strange...

00:27:51.368 --> 00:27:53.437
and that it seems
like she's refusing to wake up.

00:27:54.805 --> 00:27:56.573
I should've asked to see her sooner.

00:27:56.573 --> 00:27:59.076
She ignored my calls a few times,

00:27:59.076 --> 00:28:00.077
so I just left her alone.

00:28:00.978 --> 00:28:03.113
It was awkward for us to reach out too.

00:28:03.113 --> 00:28:05.683
We all knew what happened,
but we couldn't really take sides.

00:28:05.683 --> 00:28:07.885
But we couldn't
exactly preach at her, either.

00:28:07.885 --> 00:28:08.786
But...

00:28:09.219 --> 00:28:12.056
what could've hurt so much
that she'd take pills?

00:28:12.456 --> 00:28:13.590
It's obvious.

00:28:13.590 --> 00:28:15.259
Producer Noh probably told her
they should break up.

00:28:15.592 --> 00:28:18.762
These days, Na Jeong
and Producer Noh look really close.

00:28:21.065 --> 00:28:24.201
Is it really right to keep hiding this
from Na Jeong?

00:28:24.535 --> 00:28:25.803
Forget it.

00:28:25.803 --> 00:28:27.771
Why should we step into
something this messy?

00:28:27.771 --> 00:28:30.007
What useless talk
are you two chattering about?

00:28:33.077 --> 00:28:34.345
Do you really have that little to do?

00:28:35.379 --> 00:28:37.247
You've got that much time...

00:28:37.247 --> 00:28:39.216
to gossip about baseless
and pointless rumors?

00:28:40.250 --> 00:28:41.452
It's just...

00:28:41.452 --> 00:28:42.987
I don't care what it's about.

00:28:44.054 --> 00:28:46.090
Don't go around
spreading pointless rumors.

00:28:47.424 --> 00:28:50.527
Nothing like that
helps the company in any way.

00:28:51.295 --> 00:28:53.797
Do you want to stir up trouble
just by running your mouth?

00:29:00.638 --> 00:29:01.472
Hello.

00:29:06.176 --> 00:29:07.344
You scared me.

00:29:07.344 --> 00:29:08.812
Why? What's going on?

00:29:09.213 --> 00:29:10.080
Hey.

00:29:10.514 --> 00:29:12.650
Do you know a woman named Seon Min?

00:29:13.250 --> 00:29:14.151
Seon Min?

00:29:14.685 --> 00:29:16.387
Yeah, I've seen her.

00:29:16.687 --> 00:29:18.022
I heard she couldn't renew contract...

00:29:18.022 --> 00:29:20.791
and was having a hard time finding work.

00:29:21.091 --> 00:29:22.092
Hey, you idiot.

00:29:22.326 --> 00:29:24.528
This is not the time to be so calm.

00:29:24.528 --> 00:29:27.264
They say that woman
called Seon Min took pills.

00:29:28.299 --> 00:29:30.334
Why? Did something bad happen?

00:29:31.568 --> 00:29:33.270
Because of your husband.

00:29:33.637 --> 00:29:34.772
My husband?

00:29:35.806 --> 00:29:37.341
Tell me everything, in detail.

00:29:38.342 --> 00:29:39.677
Because of Producer Noh,

00:29:40.444 --> 00:29:42.246
Kim Seon Min took pills?

00:29:43.247 --> 00:29:45.582
No, Na Jeong, don't get the wrong idea.

00:29:45.582 --> 00:29:48.252
I was just speculating when I said that.

00:29:48.252 --> 00:29:49.486
Still,

00:29:49.486 --> 00:29:52.656
you must have had some reason
to think that, ma'am.

00:29:56.660 --> 00:29:58.195
I'm sorry, Na Jeong.

00:29:58.696 --> 00:30:00.464
Actually, for a while now,

00:30:00.464 --> 00:30:03.734
people have been saying
Producer Noh and Seon Min...

00:30:03.734 --> 00:30:05.069
were dating.

00:30:05.903 --> 00:30:07.671
I wanted to tell you,

00:30:07.671 --> 00:30:10.274
but since we didn't see it ourselves,
it felt wrong to say anything.

00:30:25.089 --> 00:30:26.957
Then why did that rumor start?

00:30:27.725 --> 00:30:29.893
There must've been something behind it.

00:30:30.527 --> 00:30:31.795
Well,

00:30:32.696 --> 00:30:35.866
some people saw Seon Min
grabbing onto Producer Noh...

00:30:35.866 --> 00:30:38.102
and crying in the conference room.

00:30:38.869 --> 00:30:41.438
And people saw them alone together
outside the office...

00:30:41.438 --> 00:30:43.140
multiple times.

00:30:43.474 --> 00:30:46.844
And a few colleagues said
that on their way out for drinks,

00:30:47.645 --> 00:30:51.782
they saw Mr. Kim, the head of division,
alone with Producer Noh.

00:30:52.750 --> 00:30:57.187
And apparently,
Mr. Kim threw a drink in his face...

00:30:57.187 --> 00:30:59.223
and said this.

00:30:59.723 --> 00:31:02.393
Don't you feel even a little sorry
for Na Jeong waiting at home?

00:31:03.093 --> 00:31:05.129
Watch yourself and behave, you punk.

00:31:30.054 --> 00:31:32.389
Don't try to dodge this,
and answer me honestly.

00:31:33.090 --> 00:31:35.693
What exactly is going on
between you and this woman, Kim Seon Min?

00:31:37.861 --> 00:31:40.130
I don't know what you heard,

00:31:40.898 --> 00:31:43.167
but it's not what you think,
so don't get the wrong idea.

00:31:43.867 --> 00:31:45.336
Like I told you before,

00:31:45.970 --> 00:31:47.404
she lost her job
and couldn't renew her contract,

00:31:47.404 --> 00:31:49.640
so I met her a few times
to connect her with people.

00:31:50.874 --> 00:31:52.309
I'll explain the details later.

00:31:52.743 --> 00:31:54.211
What are you playing at right now?

00:31:54.778 --> 00:31:58.315
I saw you with that woman myself,

00:31:58.315 --> 00:32:01.251
and everyone at work knows
you're having an affair with her.

00:32:02.152 --> 00:32:05.489
And yet you don't even think
you owe me an explanation?

00:32:06.557 --> 00:32:08.892
Do you seriously want to see me snap?

00:32:09.126 --> 00:32:11.195
