You're right.

00:53:40.084 --> 00:53:41.919
A line from a drama
just popped into my head.

00:53:42.820 --> 00:53:43.654
What?

00:53:44.254 --> 00:53:46.390
"Even if everyone else knew,

00:53:46.390 --> 00:53:48.225
I just hoped my family wouldn't."

00:54:05.309 --> 00:54:07.845
Hello, Mr. Kim.
