So I scolded him...

00:55:33.464 --> 00:55:35.165
like an older brother would.

00:55:35.165 --> 00:55:38.068
So you only heard it as a rumor too, then?

00:55:39.169 --> 00:55:40.037
Yeah.

00:55:40.504 --> 00:55:43.207
Did you call in show host Kim Seon Min
and ask her as well?

00:55:46.010 --> 00:55:47.111
Well,

00:55:47.111 --> 00:55:50.381
by then, Seon Min had already resigned.

00:55:50.381 --> 00:55:52.116
And usually, in situations like that,

00:55:52.583 --> 00:55:55.753
people assume the married man
is more at fault, not the single woman.

00:56:22.313 --> 00:56:23.981
Seon Young, it's me.

00:56:24.581 --> 00:56:27.851
Do you happen to know
which hospital Kim Seon Min is in?

00:56:40.130 --> 00:56:41.599
(Wishing you a speedy recovery,
Kim * Min)

00:56:53.177 --> 00:56:54.011
I'm sorry.

00:56:55.012 --> 00:56:55.946
Seon Min.

00:56:59.049 --> 00:57:00.751
I know you wouldn't want me here,

00:57:01.952 --> 00:57:02.987
but I came anyway.

00:57:04.788 --> 00:57:05.990
If I don't see you,

00:57:07.358 --> 00:57:09.360
