00:57:16.400 --> 00:57:17.434
I'm sorry.

00:57:17.935 --> 00:57:19.703
But I was so scared.

00:57:20.471 --> 00:57:22.539
I was scared I'd be blacklisted
in the industry.

00:57:25.909 --> 00:57:29.546
Still, why did you have to take pills?

00:57:30.648 --> 00:57:33.417
How am I supposed to live
