What did you mean by what you just said?

00:57:47.531 --> 00:57:48.565
It's nothing.

00:57:50.501 --> 00:57:51.869
Don't lie to me.

00:57:51.869 --> 00:57:53.504
You clearly know what's going on.

00:57:53.737 --> 00:57:56.674
Explain to me
why Seon Min took those pills.

00:58:00.544 --> 00:58:01.512
Ye Na.

00:58:02.179 --> 00:58:03.180
Ye Na.

