I report sexual harassment
by K, the Head of Division,

00:58:21.265 --> 00:58:22.366
at Sweet Home Shopping.

00:58:24.768 --> 00:58:25.502
(Yang Mi Sook)

00:58:27.404 --> 00:58:28.372
Mi Sook.

00:58:28.372 --> 00:58:30.541
Hey, did you see the screenshot
I sent you?

