I had a feeling
Kim Seon Min and your husband...

00:58:35.579 --> 00:58:38.882
had something shady going on,
so I sounded out Assistant Manager Ha.

00:58:38.882 --> 00:58:39.783
Assistant Manager Ha?

00:58:40.117 --> 00:58:41.518
Who's that?

00:58:41.518 --> 00:58:42.620
Didn't I tell you?

00:58:42.620 --> 00:58:44.421
Someone on the company's legal team
who's been tagging along with me lately.

00:58:45.489 --> 00:58:46.323
And?

00:58:46.890 --> 00:58:50.461
But the guy kept insisting
he didn't know a thing...

00:58:50.461 --> 00:58:52.062
and wouldn't talk no matter what.

00:58:52.396 --> 00:58:54.932
So while he stepped into the bathroom
for a minute,

00:58:55.232 --> 00:58:57.067
I secretly went through his phone,

00:58:57.067 --> 00:58:58.335
and that's what I found.

00:58:59.103 --> 00:59:00.304
So from that,

00:59:00.904 --> 00:59:03.073
it looks like it wasn't your husband
she had an affair with,

00:59:03.540 --> 00:59:04.942
but that rat-faced division head...

00:59:04.942 --> 00:59:07.111
she got tangled up with.

00:59:09.013 --> 00:59:10.214
The way I see it,

00:59:10.614 --> 00:59:13.584
your husband was just trying
to help his junior...

00:59:13.584 --> 00:59:14.918
and ended up cornered.

00:59:16.220 --> 00:59:18.122
Since it involved the higher-ups,

00:59:18.122 --> 00:59:20.024
if he said something reckless,

00:59:20.024 --> 00:59:21.692
he probably thought
he'd get his head chopped off.

00:59:22.626 --> 00:59:25.462
That's probably why
