00:59:26.797 --> 00:59:29.967
Don't I sound like a detective?

00:59:41.912 --> 00:59:43.514
And usually, in situations like that,

00:59:44.014 --> 00:59:47.184
people assume the married man
is more at fault, not the single woman.

01:00:12.276 --> 01:00:13.978
It was really tough.

01:00:15.279 --> 01:00:16.780
Seriously.

01:00:16.780 --> 01:00:19.383
Well, look at our lovely show hosts.

