We were just swapping
some scary stories from work.

01:00:27.324 --> 01:00:28.859
I'd love to hear those too.

01:00:29.627 --> 01:00:31.662
I'll set up a team dinner soon, okay?

01:00:33.130 --> 01:00:34.632
- Good work, then.
- Yes.

01:00:39.637 --> 01:00:42.940
But the way he looks at us...

01:00:42.940 --> 01:00:44.808
is kind of unsettling.

01:00:44.808 --> 01:00:46.343
Is it just me who thinks that?

01:00:46.343 --> 01:00:48.479
You too?
Honestly, me too.

