01:01:19.643 --> 01:01:21.211
Why did you drink so much?

01:01:23.714 --> 01:01:26.951
That habit you have of deciding everything
on your own without talking to me.

01:01:26.951 --> 01:01:28.385
That patriarchal attitude.

01:01:28.385 --> 01:01:29.687
Do I look that pathetic to you?

01:01:30.120 --> 01:01:30.988
That easy to push around?

01:01:31.822 --> 01:01:35.125
If I'd known you were this stubborn
and impossible to talk to,

01:01:36.493 --> 01:01:38.162
I never would've married you.

01:02:12.896 --> 01:02:15.833
(Min Woo, Min Jun's Mom)

01:02:25.309 --> 01:02:27.478
Honey, I'm sorry.

01:02:31.849 --> 01:02:33.384
You're still...

01:02:33.751 --> 01:02:36.020
the man I'd most want to be married to.

01:03:01.011 --> 01:03:01.912
About everything,

01:03:03.013 --> 01:03:04.848
I'm sorry I couldn't explain it properly.

01:03:07.418 --> 01:03:08.485
Seon Min...

01:03:09.420 --> 01:03:12.056
came to me saying
there was no one else she could trust.

01:03:13.891 --> 01:03:15.893
You and the kids kept coming to mind,

01:03:16.860 --> 01:03:19.196
but I just couldn't bring myself
to turn her away.

01:03:20.230 --> 01:03:22.032
And in the end,
I ended up flagged at work.

01:03:23.934 --> 01:03:27.004
In the middle of all that,
you said you were joining the company.

01:03:28.505 --> 01:03:30.374
And I really didn't want...

01:03:31.208 --> 01:03:33.143
you to see just how pathetic I'd been.

01:03:38.048 --> 01:03:38.949
Me too.

01:03:39.717 --> 01:03:41.952
I'm sorry for doubting you first
without knowing the full story.

01:03:44.555 --> 01:03:47.491
I should've trusted my own husband.

01:03:49.093 --> 01:03:50.728
But once I learned what really happened,

01:03:52.896 --> 01:03:54.898
it brought something back to me.

01:03:57.735 --> 01:03:58.769
You've always been...

01:04:00.037 --> 01:04:01.472
the kind of person...

01:04:01.472 --> 01:04:03.474
