01:04:15.119 --> 01:04:16.654
You had to protect your family,

01:04:17.988 --> 01:04:20.691
and still protect your conscience
in a mess like that.

01:04:23.127 --> 01:04:24.895
You must have been really torn up inside.

01:04:29.133 --> 01:04:30.134
But honey,

01:04:33.237 --> 01:04:34.805
